    <item>
      <title>英国富人受通胀和高利率打击最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/britain-s-richest-hit-most-by-inflation-and-high-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于抵押贷款成本高昂以及餐馆和酒店价格快速上涨，英国最富裕家庭经历的通货膨胀率高于社会较贫困阶层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/britain-s-richest-hit-most-by-inflation-and-high-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 10:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究警告称，美国银行存在商业地产盲点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-banks-have-a-commercial-property-blind-spot-risk-study-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究表明，由于美国大型银行向房地产投资信托提供了信贷额度和定期贷款，它们在商业地产方面的风险敞口可能比监管机构认为的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-banks-have-a-commercial-property-blind-spot-risk-study-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>获利回吐加速，基本金属价格快速回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/aluminum-hits-two-year-high-as-china-capacity-limits-help-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者在工业金属市场强劲上涨后寻求套现，铜价延续从纪录高位回落的势头，铝价也从两年高位回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/aluminum-hits-two-year-high-as-china-capacity-limits-help-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
